---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Sigrid Elnan - Om">
  <div class="about-container">
    <div class="photo-container">
      <img
        src="/src/assets/profilbilde.jpeg"
        alt="Bilde av Sigrid"
        class="profile-photo"
      />
    </div>

    <div class="about-content">
      <h1>Om meg</h1>
      <p>
        Jeg er Sigrid Greiff Elnan, en fullstack utvikler som holder til i
        Trondheim.
      </p>
      <p>
        Har egentlig ikke skjønt hva man skriver i en om-side, men etter flere
        år som utvikler tenkte jeg det var på tide med en egen nettside. Når jeg
        ikke driver med utvikling liker jeg å holde på med musikk, hovedsakelig
        fløyte og saksofon, eller mye av det som kan defineres som nerdete. Det
        vil si lesing, video spill, brettspill, ttrpgs, og binging av tv-serier
        og youtube.
      </p>

      <div class="social-links">
        <a
          href="https://github.com/sigridge"
          class="social-link"
          target="_blank"
        >
          <div class="social-icon github">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path
                d="M12 0c-6.626 0-12 5.373-12 12 0 5.302 3.438 9.8 8.207 11.387.599.111.793-.261.793-.577v-2.234c-3.338.726-4.033-1.416-4.033-1.416-.546-1.387-1.333-1.756-1.333-1.756-1.089-.745.083-.729.083-.729 1.205.084 1.839 1.237 1.839 1.237 1.07 1.834 2.807 1.304 3.492.997.107-.775.418-1.305.762-1.604-2.665-.305-5.467-1.334-5.467-5.931 0-1.311.469-2.381 1.236-3.221-.124-.303-.535-1.524.117-3.176 0 0 1.008-.322 3.301 1.23.957-.266 1.983-.399 3.003-.404 1.02.005 2.047.138 3.006.404 2.291-1.552 3.297-1.23 3.297-1.23.653 1.653.242 2.874.118 3.176.77.84 1.235 1.911 1.235 3.221 0 4.609-2.807 5.624-5.479 5.921.43.372.823 1.102.823 2.222v3.293c0 .319.192.694.801.576 4.765-1.589 8.199-6.086 8.199-11.386 0-6.627-5.373-12-12-12z"
              ></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <span class="social-text">GitHub</span>
        </a>

        <a
          href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/sigrid-greiff-elnan/"
          class="social-link"
          target="_blank"
        >
          <div class="social-icon linkedin">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path
                d="M19 0h-14c-2.761 0-5 2.239-5 5v14c0 2.761 2.239 5 5 5h14c2.762 0 5-2.239 5-5v-14c0-2.761-2.238-5-5-5zm-11 19h-3v-11h3v11zm-1.5-12.268c-.966 0-1.75-.79-1.75-1.764s.784-1.764 1.75-1.764 1.75.79 1.75 1.764-.783 1.764-1.75 1.764zm13.5 12.268h-3v-5.604c0-3.368-4-3.113-4 0v5.604h-3v-11h3v1.765c1.396-2.586 7-2.777 7 2.476v6.759z"
              ></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <span class="social-text">LinkedIn</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
  .about-container {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 3rem auto;
    padding: 2rem;
    display: flex;
    gap: 3rem;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .photo-container {
    flex: 1;
    max-width: 400px;
  }

  .profile-photo {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    border-radius: 10px;
    box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
    border: 3px solid var(--secondary-blue);
    transition:
      transform 0.3s ease,
      box-shadow 0.3s ease;
  }

  .profile-photo:hover {
    transform: scale(1.02);
    box-shadow: 0 15px 35px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
  }

  .about-content {
    flex: 1.5;
  }

  .about-content h1 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: var(--secondary-blue);
    border-bottom: 2px solid var(--secondary-blue);
    padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
    display: inline-block;
  }

  .about-content p {
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
  }

  .highlight {
    color: var(--accent);
    font-weight: bold;
  }

  .social-links {
    margin-top: 3rem;
    display: flex;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    align-items: center;
    border-top: 1px solid #3a3f44;
    padding-top: 2rem;
  }

  .social-icon {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    width: 48px;
    height: 48px;
    background-color: var(--card-bg);
    border-radius: 50%;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
  }

  .social-icon:hover {
    transform: translateY(-5px);
    box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
  }

  .github {
    background-color: #333;
  }

  .linkedin {
    background-color: #0077b5;
  }

  .social-icon svg {
    width: 24px;
    height: 24px;
    fill: white;
  }

  .social-text {
    font-weight: bold;
    margin-left: 0.5rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
  }

  .social-text:hover {
    color: var(--text);
  }

  .social-link {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    text-decoration: none;
    color: inherit;
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .about-container {
      flex-direction: column;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .photo-container {
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .about-content h1 {
      margin: 0 auto;
      display: block;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .social-links {
      justify-content: center;
    }
  }
</style>
